dc_title_s: North Sea, Germany--Netherlands, Ems River from Dukegat to Pogum (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the National Imagery and Mapping Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by spot heights. "From a German chart of 1998. Shipping list no. 2000-2005-S. Place names in German (Plattdeutsch), with glossary in English. "Copyright 1999 by the United States government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." Two insets: A. Harbor plan of Emden. Scale 1:12,500 -- B. Dollard (Dollart). Scale 1:50,000. "Soundings in meters." Map No. 37224. This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
dc_creator_sm: United States. National Imagery and Mapping Agency
